images.description: A poached egg atop a bed of kale salad in a white bowl.
Celebrity chef Gordon Ramsey cooking in an outdoor kitchen surrounded by an audience, with a woman assisting him.
A martial artist in a dobok is performing a flying side kick at a bag hanging from a tree at dusk.
Underwater photo of a black smoker, a type of hydrothermal vent, emitting a blue plume of mineral-rich water.
Aerial view of a brightly lit city at night with dense buildings and long streets.
A man in a red shirt and plaid shorts along with a helmet and is joyfully zip-lining against a backdrop of trees and sky.

Ingredients, measuring cup and a bowl sitting on a green and speckled kitchen counter.  In front of them is a cookbook, laying open to what appears to be a recipe with a picture of a pie, suggesting preparation for baking.
A cable car in San Francisco with Alcatraz Island in the background on a clear day.
A pair of brown, plush-lined boots is shown from the calf down on a gravelly surface.
